### Create a new training slot (As Coach)
POST {{host}}/api/coaches/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{coachToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2026-08-10T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-08-10T11:00:00Z"
}

### Try to create overlapping slot (Should return 500 Business Error)
POST {{host}}/api/coaches/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{coachToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2026-08-10T10:30:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-08-10T11:30:00Z"
}